parameters: \N<Girl>Huh? Who are you? I haven't seen you before.

\N<Boku>I'm Boku! I usually live in a town far away, but
during summer vacation, I stay at this \N[2] house.
\N<Girl>Oh, I see. You came from the city. I see.

\N<Girl>You should be able to tell just by looking. It's
feeding time, feeding time. Today it's my turn. Watering and
feeding.
\N<Boku>Is that so? Hey, can I do it too?

\N<Girl>You want to do something like this? Don't you have
chickens at your school in the city? Well, whatever, do as
you please.
\N<Boku>Huh? Hey, hey, tell me your name!

\N<Girl>Huh? It's Mika, Mika. This should be fine. Well
then, see you.
\N<Mika-chan>Oh, Boku? What's with the serious face?
\N<Boku>You know, I'm going back to the city tomorrow...

\N<Mika-chan>Ah, I see. So you're only here during summer
vacation, right? Well then, today is our farewell. Bye-bye!

\N<Mika-chan>What's with that? You'll come back next summer
vacation, right? It's not just summer, there's also winter
vacation and spring vacation. We can meet again anytime.

\N<Mika-chan>Next time we meet, remember that I won't lose
on the grass slide!

\N<Boku>Yeah! I won't lose either! Well then, let's meet
again, Mika-chan!

\N<Mika-chan>Oh, Boku? What are you here for? If it's
feeding time, it's already over.
ミカちゃんに会いに来たよ

\N<Mika-chan>Huh? Is that so? Haha...? I see, you're in the
mood for something naughty again, aren't you?

\N<Mika-chan>See, I knew it... ♥ I can see right through you
♥ Well, if you're going to say that much, I guess I can't
help it ♥ Then... let's go to my room ♥

\N<Mika-chan>Oh, really? I thought boys would be more
aggressive, but I guess not.
